Posting to &lt;root&gt;/users/&lt;userId&gt; assumes, as you note, that you already
have a userId.  If you do that, your client is assuming how the server
operates, rather than letting the server decide for itself.

Post to &lt;root&gt;/users, and let the response tell you what was assigned.

-Eric.

